                [
                    "description",
                    "MuddyWater leverages valid accounts obtained through phishing, credential harvesting, password spraying, or other credential theft techniques to gain and maintain access to victim environments. By abusing legitimate user credentials, the group can authenticate to systems, cloud services, and network resources while blending in with normal user activity."
